# Implementation Plan: CogniFuse Project Alignment

Align the CogniFuse application with the provided "Master Reference Document", implementing all 5 core modules and advanced technologies (GNN, GraphSAGE, SM-2, FAISS).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This plan involves installing several large dependencies: `torch-geometric`, `faiss-cpu`, and `spacy`. Please ensure your environment has ~1GB of free space.

> [!WARNING]
> The **GNN (GraphSAGE)** requires unsupervised training on the graph after it is built to generate meaningful embeddings. This will add a slight delay (a few seconds) to the initial graph building phase.

## Proposed Changes

